Fortress Investment Group

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Fortress Investment Group, LLC





Type

Public


Traded as
NYSE: FIG


Industry
Investment Management Firm: Private Equity, Credit, Liquid Markets and Traditional Asset Management


Founded
1998; 19 years ago (1998)


